description: Flights and ferries are cancelled as winds of up to 70mph cause travel chaos on the Isle of Man.
title: Bin lorry blown over as Storm Brendan rocks Isle of Man
title_page: Bin lorry blown over as Storm Brendan rocks Isle of Man - BBC News
maintext: High-sided vehicles were banned from using the Mountain Road during the gales, while other drivers were warned of a partial landslip on the carriageway.
